description: SDHC Class10 compliant. Fully compatible with the SD 2.0 Standard. Supports Micro SDHC devices and cardreader. Combined with a SDHC adapter can be used as standard SDHC memory card. Supports Content Protection for Recordable Media (CPRM). Security level complies with Secure Digital Music Initiative (SDMI). Compliant with RoHS requirement.
title: AmazonBasics 32 GB microSDHC Class 10 Flash Memory Card with SD Adapter
